deskutils/lazylibrarian includes an RC script:
%%PREFIX%%/etc/rc.d/lazylibrarian

TO START LAZYLIBRARIAN ON BOOT:
echo 'lazylibrarian_enable="YES"' >> /etc/rc.conf

START MANUALLY:
%%PREFIX%%/etc/rc.d/lazylibrarian start

Once started, visit the following to configure:
http://localhost:8082/

